            "title": "5月零售回升2.4% 業界：續轉佳",
            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2025年7月3日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">5月零售回升2.4% 業界：續轉佳<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/07/03/4128797_7210b15474a6bfc4ab322a1b24842034.png\" title=\"近月訪港旅客增加，帶動本港零售市道回暖。（黃勁璋攝）\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/07/03/4128797_7210b15474a6bfc4ab322a1b24842034_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/07/03/4128797_7210b15474a6bfc4ab322a1b24842034.png\" title=\"近月訪港旅客增加，帶動本港零售市道回暖。（黃勁璋攝）\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/07/03/4128797_7210b15474a6bfc4ab322a1b24842034.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"近月訪港旅客增加，帶動本港零售市道回暖。（黃勁璋攝）\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n受惠大型演唱會帶動訪港旅客增多，加上低基數效應，本港零售業經歷了連續14個月下跌後，終於止跌回升。政府統計處昨日公布，5月的零售業總銷貨價值臨時估計為313.2億元，按年升2.4%，優於市場預期跌1.8%，銷貨量也增1.9%。香港零售管理協會表示，相信零售市道不會再下沉，往後月份逐步向上。\n終止連跌...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
            "link": "https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/headline/article/4128797/5%E6%9C%88%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%9B%9E%E5%8D%872.4%25+%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%8C%E8%BD%89%E4%BD%B3",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-03 02:44:34",
            "source": "hkej",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
